snippet.title: PlayStation® All-Stars Island app - Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Download from Google Play - http://bit.ly/1ceYF0V
Download from the App Store - http://bit.ly/132xkuP
Get the free PlayStation® All-Stars Island app on your smartphone or tablet (iOS and Android only) to play the first unlocked game, Uncharted™: Drake's Pursuit. 

Available in Austria, Belgium, Denmark, Finland, France, Iceland, Ireland, Netherlands, Sweden, Switzerland and the UK.

More games will be available to download through updates soon.

#PlayStationIsland
